{"tid":836622,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"我係腎虛還是腎虧⋯⋯","createTime":"2018-09-25T19:47:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T10:24:24.000Z","uid":125655,"like":3,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"7fc9638ca358c208db65de59dfbaa9f9704bf26b","tid":836622,"uid":125655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T19:47:56.000Z","msg":"小弟手淫十年，呢幾日幾乎日期，都有打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一直都係A0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 前幾排同班F去佐叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當我除曬褲戴埋套，點知就扯唔起了⋯⋯<br />\n上網查佐下感覺係虛⋯⋯但都男人最痛呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n症狀：畏寒怕凍，吹冷氣時手腳都容易凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n扯旗覺得充唔到血比細佬，姐係頂唔起來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好容易出汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n坐耐少少腰痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等等⋯⋯<br />\n我依家開始戒J嘎喇⋯⋯<br />\n各位幫我分析下係腎虛定腎虧，衰虛都好過虧呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\np.s:打算食六味地黃丸and澳洲只bio island的袋鼠丸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f02da33c23e91a649d489074e9a5006df52574f0","tid":836622,"uid":85659,"like":103,"dislike":2,"score":101,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T19:50:20.000Z","msg":"小弟1日2次，由12歲keep到31都無你既問題<br />\n應該係你個野壞左"},{"pid":"6baad85500507c9ad20aaff1f6fe57b8cad6e3ca","tid":836622,"uid":125655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f02da33c23e91a649d489074e9a5006df52574f0","tid":836622,"uid":85659,"like":103,"dislike":2,"score":101,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T19:50:20.000Z","msg":"小弟1日2次，由12歲keep到31都無你既問題<br />\n應該係你個野壞左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T19:53:37.000Z","msg":"你身體好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gi